# Leave DATABASE_URL unset to use the built-in embedded Postgres (PGlite),
# seeded from src/data/alpha_seed.json on startup. Great for local dev and a
# free, zero-config deploy.
#
# For a persistent production database (so saved profiles survive), create a
# free Neon Postgres (https://neon.tech) and paste its connection string here.
# The data layer will use it automatically and the seed will load into it.
# DATABASE_URL="postgresql://user:password@host/db?sslmode=require"
